'''Sander Tangvik''' (born 29 November 2002) is a Norwegian [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] for German {{German football updater|Hamburg}} club [[Hamburger SV]] and the [[Norway national football team|Norway national team]].

==Club career==

In March 2021 Tangvik signed a new contract with Rosenborg and became a part of the first team squad.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.rbk.no/nyheter/dette-er-noe-jeg-har-trent-for-hele-livet|title=Dette er noe jeg har trent for hele livet|date=4 March 2021|publisher=RBK.no|access-date=6 November 2022}}</ref> Later that year in August he made his debut against [[Orkla Fotballklubb|Orkla]] in the [[2021–22 Norwegian Football Cup|Norwegian Cup]], coming on for the second half.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nidaros.no/sander-fikk-rbk-debuten-etter-27-turer-pa-benken-jeg-har-ventet-en-stund-ja/s/5-113-222221|title=Sander fikk RBK debuten etter 27 turer på benken - Jeg har ventet en stund ja|date=1 August 2021|publisher=Nidaros.no|access-date=7 November 2022}}</ref>

Tangvik made his league debut on 6 November 2022 coming on in the 89th minute against [[FK Jerv|Jerv]], replacing [[André Hansen]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.rbk.no/nyheter/sikret-europakvalifisering-borte-mot-jerv|title=Sikret Europakvalifisering borte mot Jerv|date=6 November 2022|publisher=RBK.no|access-date=6 November 2022}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nidaros.no/rbk-gjorde-jobben-na-venter-charterbillet-til-europa/s/5-113-383274|title=RBK gjorde jobben – nå venter charterbillet til Europa|date=6 November 2022|publisher=RBK.no|access-date=7 November 2022}}</ref>

On 22 January 2026, Tangvik signed with [[Hamburger SV]] in Germany.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Hamburger SV|url=https://www.hsv.de/en/news/hsv-sign-sander-tangvik|title=HSV sign Sander Tangvik|date=22 January 2026|access-date=22 January 2026}}</ref>
He made his debut in a 1-1 match against [[Bayer 04 Leverkusen]] on the last day of the [[2025–26 Bundesliga|2025-26]]-season, where he also saved a penalty against [[Patrik Schick]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hsv.de/news/sander-tangvik-eine-mehr-als-gelungene-premiere|title=Sander Tangvik: Eine mehr als gelungene premiere|publisher=HSV|language=de|date=18 May 2026}}</ref>

